# Automation Scripts

## Overview
Collection of shell scripts for WordPress setup, maintenance, and content management.

## Core Scripts
- **Website Setup**: [scripts/create-website-structure.sh](mdc:scripts/create-website-structure.sh) - Create pages and structure
- **News System**: [scripts/create-news-content.sh](mdc:scripts/create-news-content.sh) - News content creation
- **Menu Setup**: [scripts/setup-news-menu.sh](mdc:scripts/setup-news-menu.sh) - Navigation menu configuration
- **WooCommerce**: [scripts/setup-woocommerce.sh](mdc:scripts/setup-woocommerce.sh) - E-commerce setup

## Content Management
### News System
- **Content Creation**: [scripts/create-news-content.sh](mdc:scripts/create-news-content.sh) - Generate news articles
- **Menu Configuration**: [scripts/setup-news-menu.sh](mdc:scripts/setup-news-menu.sh) - News navigation
- **URL Fixes**: [scripts/fix-news-url.sh](mdc:scripts/fix-news-url.sh) - URL optimization
- **Submenu Setup**: [scripts/create-news-submenu.sh](mdc:scripts/create-news-submenu.sh) - Submenu structure

### Page Management
- **Simple Pages**: [scripts/create-pages-simple.sh](mdc:scripts/create-pages-simple.sh) - Basic page creation
- **Policy Pages**: [scripts/update-policy-pages.sh](mdc:scripts/update-policy-pages.sh) - Legal content updates
- **Menu Fixes**: [scripts/fix-menu-completely.sh](mdc:scripts/fix-menu-completely.sh) - Menu structure fixes

## System Maintenance
### Docker Management
- **Permissions Fix**: [scripts/docker-fix-permissions.sh](mdc:scripts/docker-fix-permissions.sh) - Fix file permissions
- **Alternative Fix**: [scripts/fix-docker-permissions.sh](mdc:scripts/fix-docker-permissions.sh) - Alternative permission fix

### WordPress Management
- **Menu Configuration**: [scripts/fix-menu-according-to-docs.sh](mdc:scripts/fix-menu-according-to-docs.sh) - Menu alignment
- **URL Optimization**: [scripts/fix-news-page-url.sh](mdc:scripts/fix-news-page-url.sh) - URL structure fixes

## Usage Examples
```bash
# Create website structure
./scripts/create-website-structure.sh

# Setup news system
./scripts/create-news-content.sh
./scripts/setup-news-menu.sh

# Fix permissions
./scripts/docker-fix-permissions.sh

# Setup WooCommerce
./scripts/setup-woocommerce.sh
```

