## Script Features
- **Error Handling**: Proper error checking and reporting
- **Logging**: Detailed execution logs
- **Idempotent**: Safe to run multiple times
- **Docker Integration**: Works within Docker environment
- **WP CLI Integration**: Uses WordPress command-line interface
